</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_45" id="21r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_45_line_1574102033693_198">F von Seldeneck</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_45_r1l8"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> fridrich / vns hat fürgelegt fraw Anna die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l9"><expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Schopperin <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burgerin / vvie daʒ Fricʒ krug </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l10">von Rotendorff ir Armman vor Hanſen Triller </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l12"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> diener vnſicher ſeẏ / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l13"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> diener daran weẏſen wöllet / daʒ Er der <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l14"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Burgerın ıren armman ſicher auff freuntlıch reht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l15">das wollen etc / vnd het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> derſelb ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l16">cʒu <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ vnſerr <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> <expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>cʒeſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l20"> <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> wil 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſie Jm </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_45_line_1574102355974_243">
<del rend="strikethrough">die <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ vnſer <expan>B<ex>urgerin</ex></expan> / <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> ~ dıener </del></ab></add> oder <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> ſcheimboten mıt <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l22"><expan>völle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte 
<add><ab facs="#facs_45_r1l21">von dem <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> irm <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogens</expan> ſleunigs rechten gern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l23">helffen <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie des ermant wirdt / vnd lat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l24">des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freuntlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıder wiſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_line_1574102504805_265">beẏ diſem boten / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Georij Anno octauo </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_45" id="21r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan cert="high">F<ex>ridrich</ex></expan> von Seldeneck </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Fridrich, uns hat fürgelegt fraw Anna, die
                                <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Schopperin,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin, wie daz Fricz Krug von
                        Rotendorff, ir armman, vor Hansen Triller, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
                        diener, unsicher sey. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, daran weysen wöllet, daz er der <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin, iren armman sicher auff
                        freuntlich reht, das wollen etc. Und het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        derselb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> diener czu
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> unserr
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>czespreche<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wil oder
                            <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> scheimboten mit
                            <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>völle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte <add>von dem
                                    <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, irm
                                <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan></add>,
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> sleunigs rechten gern helffen,
                                <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> sie des ermant wirdt; und lat uns des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freuntlich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen bey disem boten.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Georii anno octavo.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
